								<div class="Grid__cell d:f h:full m-b:.5 m-b:0@md w:12"></div>

								<div class="Grid__cell flx-s:1 p-r:4">
									<p>
											Now I shall show you something here.
											And I&#39;ll explain.
											As you can see,
											that&#39;s a pinhead.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
